"```sql\nSELECT posts.Id AS PostId, comments.Text AS CommentText\nFROM posts\nJOIN comments ON posts.Id = comments.PostId\nWHERE posts.Title = 'Group differences on a five point Likert item';\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the post ID and the text of comments for the post titled \"Group differences on a five point Likert item\" by joining the `posts` and `comments` tables on the `PostId`."